NMAP->The best tool to scann 
https://github.com/nmap/nmap

netdiscover->Send get IP address in own network

curl -4 ifconfig.me->Get IPv4 public

-Pn->No ping
-sU->UDP port scan
-p->Port -p80,443 or -p1-1000
-F->Most useful ports
-v->Know what happen in bg
-oN test.txt->Convert the input en txt
-oX test.xml->Convert the input en xml

Agresive scan:
-sV->Get specific versions
-O->Get OS
-sC->Run scripst in each port to get more information
-T5->Don't recommended
